Package com.fastasyncworldedit.core.math

Class BlockVectorSet

java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractCollection<BlockVector3>
com.fastasyncworldedit.core.math.BlockVectorSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
BlockVector3Set, Iterable<BlockVector3>, Collection<BlockVector3>, Set<BlockVector3>
public class BlockVectorSet extends AbstractCollection<BlockVector3> implements BlockVector3Set
The BlockVectorSet is a memory optimized Set for storing BlockVector3's.

It uses about 8 bytes of memory for every 64 BlockVector3s (about 800 times less than a HashSet.
